      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s analog era, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically flawless, having undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including a VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise, short-throw engagement, paired with a rear-axle limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed for high-speed stability. Presented in showroom condition with a pristine undercarriage and original paint depth, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
